SectionStartBehavior: Specifies what should happen to the niagara system from before the section evaluates up until the first frame of the section.
SectionEvaluateBehavior: Specifies what should happen to the niagara system when section is evaluating from the 2nd frame until the last frame.
SectionEndBehavior: Specifies what should happen to the niagara system when section evaluation finishes.
AgeUpdateMode: Specifies how sequencer should update the age of the controlled niagara system.
